title: Clay and Buck’s Countdown to Election Day Episode 2 - Oct 2 2022

description:
Four great candidates from across the country -- Heidi Ganahl (CO), General Don Bolduc (NH), Rep. Lee Zeldin (NY), Dr. Scott Jensen (MN) -- and election analysis from Ann Coulter that will crack you up.
